OL,3,CCPR questions to be added to driving
OL,4,Ctheory test
OL,6,FLearner drivers are to be quizzed on
OL,7,Ftheir CPR skills in an update to the
OL,8,Ftheory test.
OL,10,FThe Driver and Vehicle Standards
OL,11,FAgency (DVSA) ` which oversees driving
OL,12,Ftests in Britain ` said motorists are
OL,13,Foften "first on the scene" when
OL,14,Fsomeone suffers a cardiac arrest.
OL,16,FAdding questions on CPR and
OL,17,Fdefibrillators to the theory test from
OL,18,Fearly next year means candidates will
OL,19,F"have a better understanding of the
OL,20,Fskills to use in an emergency", it
OL,21,Fadded.
