OL,6,FMore than 40,000 people in the UK
OL,7,Fsuffer an out-of-hospital cardiac
OL,8,Farrest each year, with fewer than one
OL,9,Fin 10 surviving.
OL,11,FResearch has found survival rates can
OL,12,Fbe as high as 70% if CPR is given and
OL,13,Fa defibrillator used within three to
OL,14,Ffive minutes of collapse.
OL,16,FDVSA chief driving examiner Mark Winn
OL,17,Fsaid: "Part of being a safe and
OL,18,Fresponsible driver is knowing what to
OL,19,Fdo in an emergency ` how to step in
OL,20,Fand make a real, life-saving
OL,21,Fdifference.
