OL,6,F"Learning CPR and how to use a
OL,7,Fdefibrillator is a very simple skill,
OL,8,Fand adding this into the official
OL,9,Flearning resource is a great way for
OL,10,FDVSA to support the drive to raise
OL,11,Fawareness."
OL,13,FThe push for the change was led by
OL,14,FProfessor Len Nokes ` chair of the
OL,15,FSave a Life Cymru scheme ` whose 24-
OL,16,Fyear-old daughter Claire died in 2017
OL,17,Ffrom complications following a cardiac
OL,18,Farrest.
