OL,6,FHe said: "When Claire, my daughter,
OL,7,Fhad her cardiac arrest, some knowledge
OL,8,Fof CPR might have made a difference.
OL,10,F"I don't want any other family to go
OL,11,Fthrough this experience.
OL,13,F"All of us in this partnership hope
OL,14,Fthat by making CPR and how to use a
OL,15,Fdefibrillator part of the theory test,
OL,16,Fwe will be able to significantly
OL,17,Fincrease the number of people who have
OL,18,Fthis life-saving awareness."
