OL,6,FJames Cant, chief executive of charity
OL,7,FResuscitation Council UK, said: "By
OL,8,Fembedding these life-saving skills
OL,9,Finto such a widely-taken assessment,
OL,10,Fwe can help ensure that more people,
OL,11,Ffrom all communities, gain the
OL,12,Fknowledge and confidence to act during
OL,13,Fa cardiac arrest."
OL,15,FLearners must pass the theory driving
OL,16,Ftest before booking a practical test.
