OL,3,CCPR questions to be added to driving
OL,4,Ctheory test
OL,6,FTheory test candidates are required to
OL,7,Fget at least 43 out of 50 multiple-
OL,8,Fchoice questions correct, covering
OL,9,Fareas such as road signs, traffic
OL,10,Flaws, vehicle safety and first aid.
OL,12,FThey must also pass a hazard
OL,13,Fperception video test.
OL,15,FMore than two million theory tests are
OL,16,Ftaken each year, with a pass rate of
OL,17,Fabout 45%.
